    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>全球控制</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个小据点开始，在世界各地建立你的网络。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个国家都意味着新的机会、新的风险和新的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你越壮大，就越显眼。<br>越显眼，就越容易成为目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/31340deceb85b7628b8efaa519ba0443.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/31340deceb85b7628b8efaa519ba0443.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/31340deceb85b7628b8efaa519ba0443.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💰 <strong>在黑钱与干净资金之间取得平衡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >干净的钱是安全的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑钱是强大的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑钱不能直接使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须洗钱、隐藏，或者承担风险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速获利会留下更多痕迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安全的方式则需要时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/dd1c567c301fa88efa1318d037f55a2d.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/dd1c567c301fa88efa1318d037f55a2d.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/dd1c567c301fa88efa1318d037f55a2d.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>决策</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有正确的决策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/909ec197f7a8a3851cdb7e3b1a71a088.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/909ec197f7a8a3851cdb7e3b1a71a088.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/909ec197f7a8a3851cdb7e3b1a71a088.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥 <strong>特工管理</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特工不是数字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们有欲望、缺陷和极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练他们，指派任务，提升他们……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/76f69332acd5a470ae5b784d85bf31d5.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/76f69332acd5a470ae5b784d85bf31d5.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/76f69332acd5a470ae5b784d85bf31d5.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>任务与行动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次行动都是一次风险计算。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队实力、选择的特工以及运气决定结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成功让你壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失败让你暴露。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/28f54f898ead4821d7f7b61ed8fdf89d.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/28f54f898ead4821d7f7b61ed8fdf89d.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/28f54f898ead4821d7f7b61ed8fdf89d.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏭 <strong>供应链</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生产、储存、分发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立实验室，生产产品，管理仓库，并进行合同运输。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次运输中，你都要决定物流、安全和贿赂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大型运输带来巨额利润。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但也会吸引更大的注意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/c7067460924670e7761d3e4fbb6e9f38.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/c7067460924670e7761d3e4fbb6e9f38.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/c7067460924670e7761d3e4fbb6e9f38.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🃏 <strong>卡牌战斗与敌对帮派</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与敌对帮派的冲突不可避免。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些冲突通过使用行动中获得的卡牌进行战略卡牌战斗来解决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以战斗、谈判，或者撤退。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/4f9200bf07a8080559ce655d3ca5ac51.poster.avif?t=1771633275\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/4f9200bf07a8080559ce655d3ca5ac51.webm?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318970/extras/4f9200bf07a8080559ce655d3ca5ac51.mp4?t=1771633275\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚨 <strong>警方压力与调查</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次非法行为都会增加警方压力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高压力会引发突袭和调查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以争取时间、清除痕迹或做出牺牲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在被监视的情况下，没有任何保证。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📈 <strong>成长与专精</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚钱让你得以生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但想要成长，你必须采取行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你选择专精的道路，完全由你决定。</p>",
